{"tid":2260233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新疆上海雲南均有武漢肺炎疫情","createTime":"2020-10-27T12:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T13:00:11.000Z","uid":122940,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"485edf15e0969211c0797fb2a082d0daebf9c34f","tid":2260233,"uid":122940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:21:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-10-27/61232755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-10-27%2F61232755&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=8bd446be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-10-27/61232755</a><br />\n雲南有些二三線城市爆發中共病毒疫情，但當地隱瞞疫情消息<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/436348?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F436348%3Flang%3Db5&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=1997bbdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/436348?lang=b5</a><br />\n網傳上海浦東新區一居家隔離人員被確診感染中共病毒（武漢肺炎），此人已導致5人確診，30多戶被集中隔離。官方否認，稱該病例未造成擴散。但外界仍心存疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/10/25/n12500493.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F10%2F25%2Fn12500493.htm&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=5f1addb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/10/25/n12500493.htm</a><br />\n10月24日，新疆喀什官方稱有1例新增中共病毒（武漢肺炎）無症狀感染者，但25日就新增了137例，該地區各中小學、幼兒園停課。有網民認為官方聲稱的「無症狀感染」是在「玩文字遊戲」，並質問：「這之前得瞞報了多久啊？」"},{"pid":"b48a26fbb5ab885b6160975958433ae3bc3a6ad7","tid":2260233,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"無事嘅 支国有齊「健康綠碼」同全民「核酸」檢查驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee774fc8a986097da91608288c9b02c888281d2","tid":2260233,"uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:23:42.000Z","msg":"全部大紀元，可信度仲衰過郭文貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722e7e897116bc7ffcb626292c28c69600746020","tid":2260233,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:23:52.000Z","msg":"支那唔係0感染咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4d5fc224db4ab1ca5526eb91aeb025951f09f7","tid":2260233,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:23:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc65e9912207deaa01c1cb1c1814eb1ad4625de0","tid":2260233,"uid":122940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cee774fc8a986097da91608288c9b02c888281d2","tid":2260233,"uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:23:42.000Z","msg":"全部大紀元，可信度仲衰過郭文貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"但中共資訊同大紀元之間，唯有信大紀元"}]}